  "conclusion": "DA provides its strongest advantage (>3\u00d7) when weight signs are imbalanced (|bias| > 0.4). In the worst case (balanced signs), DA degrades to IA. However, trained KANs naturally develop sign structure through optimization \u2014 the DA ratio for CWRU-trained KAN [28,16,4] is 3.1\u00d7. Random weights show 1.0-1.5\u00d7, confirming that training, not architecture, drives the DA advantage."
